Name: Transaction File Date
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - Daily Files" Preset Charset > tx_file_date
Description: Date derived from transaction_file_id (YYYY-MM-DD format).

Name: Transaction Count
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - Daily Files" Preset Charset > tx_count
Description: Total number of transactions per transaction file.

Name: Unique FI Count
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - Daily Files" Preset Charset > fiid_count
Description: Number of distinct financial institutions represented in the transaction file.

Name: Unique Consumer Count
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - Daily Files" Preset Charset > consumer_count
Description: Number of distinct consumers (based on account_id) in the transaction file.

Name: Oldest Transaction Date
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - Daily Files" Preset Charset > oldest_tx
Description: Earliest transaction posting date found in the file.

Name: Newest Transaction Date
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - Daily Files" Preset Charset > newest_tx
Description: Most recent transaction posting date found in the file.

Name: Historical Transaction Count
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - FIID Report" Preset Charset > historical_tx_count
Description: Number of transactions from historical files (transaction_file_id with 'D').

Name: Daily Transaction Count
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - FIID Report" Preset Charset > daily_tx_count
Description: Number of transactions from daily files (transaction_file_id not containing 'D').

Name: Historical 90-Day Transaction Count
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - FIID Report" Preset Charset > historical_90_day_tx_count
Description: Number of transactions from “ENROLLED” historical 90-day files.

Name: Oldest Transaction Date
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - FIID Report" Preset Charset > oldest_tx
Description: Earliest transaction posting date observed for the FI.

Name: Newest Transaction Date
Available Sources: "Plink Tx Report - FIID Report" Preset Charset > newest_tx
Description: Most recent transaction posting date observed for the FI.

Name: Transaction Count
Available Sources: "Plink Transaction Reports DS" Preset Charset > tx_count
Description: Total number of transactions per FI and transaction file.

Name: Consumer Count
Available Sources: "Plink Transaction Reports DS" Preset Charset > consumer_count
Description: Number of distinct consumers (based on account_id) per FI and transaction file.

Name: Oldest Transaction Date
Available Sources: "Plink Transaction Reports DS" Preset Charset > oldest_tx
Description: Earliest transaction posting date observed per FI and transaction file.

Name: Newest Transaction Date
Available Sources: "Plink Transaction Reports DS" Preset Charset > newest_tx
Description: Most recent transaction posting date observed per FI and transaction file.

Name: Total Spend
Available Sources: "Plink Transaction Reports DS" Preset Charset > total_spend
Description: Total dollar amount of all transactions per FI and transaction file.

Name: Purchase Rewards Enrolled
Available Sources: "Test Tracking - FI Summary" Preset Charset > "Purchase Rewards Enrolled"
Description: Number of consumers enrolled in purchase rewards for the FI.

Name: Total Campaign Views by Local Transactors Last 30 days
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Campaign views by local transactors (30 days)" > count
Description: Number of campaign views from consumers who transacted in the last 30 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Total Campaign Views by Local Transactors Last 7 days
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Campaign views by local transactors (7 days)" > count
Description: Number of campaign views from consumers who transacted in the last 7 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Total Local Transactor Transaction Count (30 days)
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Local Transactors (30 days)" > tx_count
Description: Total local transaction count for a consumer who transacted in the last 30 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Total Local Transactor Transaction Count (7 days)
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Local Transactors (7 days)" > tx_count
Description: Total local transaction count for a consumer who transacted in the last 7 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Oauths by Local Transactors Last 30 days
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Oauths by Local Transactors (30 days)" > oauth_count
Description: Total OAuths (Plink sign-ins) count for a consumer who transacted locally in the last 30 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Oauths by Local Transactors Last 7 days
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Oauths by Local Transactors (7 days)" > oauth_count
Description: Total OAuths (Plink sign-ins) count for a consumer who transacted locally in the last 7 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Activations by Local Transactors Last 30 days
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Activations by local transactors (30 days)" > count
Description: Campaign opt-ins count for a consumer who transacted locally in the last 30 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Activations by Local Transactors Last 7 days
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Activations by local transactors (7 days)" > count
Description: Campaign opt-ins count for a consumer who transacted locally in the last 7 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Redemptions by Local Transactors Last 30 days
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Redemptions by local transactors (30 days)" > redemption_count
Description: Campaign redemption count for a consumer who transacted locally in the last 30 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).

Name: Redemptions by Local Transactors Last 7 days
Available Sources: "Platinum Test - Redemptions by local transactors (7 days)" > redemption_count
Description: Campaign redemption count for a consumer who transacted locally in the last 7 days (trx_type = IN_SCOPE, non-aggregated merchants).
